            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">17th November [1870] ¶ Sir ¶  ¶ I have the honor by direction of the above Committee to acknowledge your letter of the 17th of November ¶  and with reference thereto to request from you a detailed acc...</supplied>
